folder: Pineapple Street & Willow Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
The front of the page says, "New Lots Avenue"

Pineapple Street, south side, east from Willow Street. At right foreground is the home of Samuel Rowland, at 79 Willow Street.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
